“日历年”通常被视为 Exempt Individual。 比如你是 2021 年入境，那么 2021, 2022, 2023, 2024, 2025 这五年你都是 Non-resident。 即使你在 2025 年进入了 ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"STEM 延期"}],"，只要没超过 5 年，你依然需要填 8843。"]}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-6 text-brand-ink","children":"手把手教你填 2026 最新 Form 8843"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"my-8 flex justify-center","children":["$","$Ld",null,{"src":"/images/form-8843-sample.webp","alt":"IRS Form 8843 Sample for 2025 Tax Year - Official Statement for Exempt Individuals and Individuals with a Medical Condition","width":1200,"height":1600,"className":"rounded-2xl border border-brand-pink/30 shadow-lg"}]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-brand-ink/75","children":["Form 8843 分为几个部分，学生（F/J/M/Q）通常只需要关注 ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"Part I"}]," 和 ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"Part III"}],"。"]}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4","children":"Part I: General Information"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-brand-ink/75","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Name & Address:"}]," 填写你目前的住址，通常是美国地址。"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"SSN/ITIN:"}]," 如果你有 OPT 收入通常会有 SSN；如果没有收入且没有 SSN，这一项可以留空。"]}]]}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4","children":"Part III: Students"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-brand-ink/75","children":"这一部分是针对 F1 / OPT 同学的核心："}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-brand-ink/75","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Line 9:"}]," 填写你 2025 年入境时的签证类型（F-1）。"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Line 10:"}]," 填写你的 F-1 身份类别（学生）。"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Line 11-12:"}]," 填写你的学校信息、联系人（通常是学校的 DSO）。"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Line 14:"}]," 统计近几年的居住天数。这是防止你被误认作 Resident 的关键项。"]}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"className